</guid></item><item><title>央行与债券多头对峙，中国债券市场动荡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-bond-market-rattled-central-bank-squares-off-with-bond-bulls-2024-08-12/</link><description>中国央行一再警告称，随着投资者追逐政府债券、逃离动荡的股票和不断下滑的房地产市场，可能存在破坏稳定的泡沫风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 00:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-bond-market-rattled-central-bank-squares-off-with-bond-bulls-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>壳牌与中石油将扩建澳大利亚苏拉特煤层气项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/shell-invest-phase-2-surat-gas-project-australia-2024-08-12/</link><description>英国石油和天然气巨头壳牌和中石油周一表示，在呼吁增加投资以增加当地能源供应的背景下，壳牌和中石油已决定扩大昆士兰州苏拉特煤层气项目（SGP）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 00:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/shell-invest-phase-2-surat-gas-project-australia-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>外交部长表示，中国支持伊朗捍卫安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-supports-iran-defending-security-says-foreign-minister-2024-08-11/</link><description>据中国外交部的一份声明称，中国外交部长王毅周日在电话中告诉伊朗代理外长，中国支持伊朗捍卫其“主权、安全和民族尊严”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 11:21:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-supports-iran-defending-security-says-foreign-minister-2024-08-11/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国空军的行动“非法”、“鲁莽”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-actions-china-air-force-illegal-reckless-2024-08-11/</link><description>中国表示，菲律宾扰乱了其训练，并指责马尼拉“非法侵入”其领空。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 06:39:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-actions-china-air-force-illegal-reckless-2024-08-11/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾与中国就南海问题进行贸易指责</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-condemns-china-air-force-dangerous-acts-south-china-sea-2024-08-10/</link><description>这是自2022年小费迪南德·马科斯总统就职以来菲律宾首次抱怨中国飞机的危险行为。</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 09:26:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-condemns-china-air-force-dangerous-acts-south-china-sea-2024-08-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国火箭解体使1000多颗卫星和其他物体面临危险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinese-rockets-breakup-puts-over-1000-satellites-other-objects-risk-2024-08-09/</link><description>分析人士周五表示，中国的一枚火箭级本周在太空中解体，产生了 700 多块碎片，使地球轨道交通繁忙区域的 1000 多颗卫星和其他物体面临危险碰撞的风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 22:03:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinese-rockets-breakup-puts-over-1000-satellites-other-objects-risk-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>央行称将增加国债交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-says-it-will-increase-treasury-bond-trading-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国人民银行还将寻求降低企业融资和家庭信贷成本。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 18:47:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-says-it-will-increase-treasury-bond-trading-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟高管表示调查仍在继续，相信其中国电动汽车措施符合世贸组织</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-executive-confident-its-chinese-ev-measures-comply-with-wto-says-probe-2024-08-09/</link><description>欧盟执行机构周五表示，欧盟委员会相信其对中国电动汽车国家补贴的调查和针对中国电动汽车补贴的措施符合世界贸易组织的规则，并将继续进行调查。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 15:37:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-executive-confident-its-chinese-ev-measures-comply-with-wto-says-probe-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大清算人要求投资者参与重组程序</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-evergrandes-liquidators-ask-investors-join-restructuring-process-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国恒大在周五提交的文件中表示，其清算人已邀请有兴趣重组这家负债累累的房地产开发商或其任何部分的投资者。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 12:48:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-evergrandes-liquidators-ask-investors-join-restructuring-process-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾与越南举行首次海岸警卫队联合演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-hold-first-ever-joint-coast-guard-exercise-2024-08-09/</link><description>周五，菲律宾和越南船只的船员用水炮轰击一艘船只，并模拟搜救，这是两国海岸警卫队在南海与北京对峙的首次联合演习。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 12:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-hold-first-ever-joint-coast-guard-exercise-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国商务部称欧盟电动汽车初裁违反世贸组织规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eus-ev-preliminary-ruling-violate-wto-rules-china-ministry-says-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国商务部周五表示，欧盟对进口电动汽车（EV）的初步裁决缺乏事实和法律依据，严重违反世界贸易组织（WTO）规则。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 09:40:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eus-ev-preliminary-ruling-violate-wto-rules-china-ministry-says-2024-08-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>